gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

The mantra of Lord Krishna was spoken to my ear, Shyam became calm like a cloud; 
After that, Brahmin-like I am established in my mind, I have remained mindful of the divine.

Here are the translations:

After God has perfected another, He is worshiped by many forms; 
After going from there, friends together, with God's company, many become perfect.
